rder process implicitly and show that for weak\nspin-fermion coupling the small-momentum transfer is mediated by a composite\npropagator. Employing the conventional diagrammatic approach to impurity\nscattering, we find the correction $\\delta \\sigma \\sim +\\ln^2 T$ for\ntemperatures above an exponentially small crossover scale.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Jul 2015 17:13:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 13 Feb 2016 11:42:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-02-16"}
