gnal, with the\nlow- and high-J lines weakening by 2-20% and 10-45%, respectively, over the\nredshift range 4 < z < 10.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Jul 2015 20:00:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 14 Oct 2015 20:00:15 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 21 Oct 2015 14:22:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-22"}
