fe by the\nformation of an annihilation pion/proton star. This unique event structure will\ndeliver a nearly background free detection possibility.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Jul 2015 21:15:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 13 Aug 2015 19:26:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-08-14"}
