illimiter, whereas on stable equilibrium\npoints they are of order of a few millimiters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Jul 2015 13:55:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 9 Sep 2015 14:21:18 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 12 May 2016 12:41:45 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sun, 15 May 2016 16:27:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-17"}
